    {
      "step_id": 5,
      "title": "",
      "instruction": "Warm complete culture medium to 37 °C. Dilute CellROX Green reagent directly into the culture medium , resulting in a final concentration of 1µM. Note: for microglia we change half medium only, so the conentration of the solution will be 2µM, to have 1µM as final concentration on cells",
